  keywords={Biodegradable plastic mulch films, Cultivated soil, Plastic-degrading yeast enzyme, Poly(butylene succinate-co-adipate), Soil esterase activities, Soil microorganisms, Biodegradable Plastics, Esterases, Microbiota, Plastics, Polyesters, Saccharomyces cerevisiae, Soil, Bacteria, Biodegradable polymers, Biodegradation, Butenes, Esters, Soils, Yeast, biodegradable plastic, esterase, plastic, polyester, Biodegradable plastic mulch film, Biodegradable plastics, Cultivated soils, Esterase activities, Mulch films, Plastic mulch, Plastic-degrading yeast enzyme, Poly(butylene succinate-co-adipate), Soil esterase activity, Soil micro-organisms, biodegradation, cultivation, enzyme activity, film, microbial community, phyllosphere, polymer, soil microorganism, yeast, metabolism, microflora, Saccharomyces cerevisiae, soil, Enzymes},
