  keywords={4-endoglucanase, Arctic, Bioprospecting, Diversity, Mycology, Svalbard, β1, Arctic, Ny-Alesund, Spitsbergen, Svalbard, Svalbard and Jan Mayen, Acremonium (Ascomycota), Arthrinium, Aspergillus, Aspergillus aculeatus, Cladosporium, Corynespora, Emericella, Emericella nidulans, Fungi, Geomyces, Hyphomycetes, Mortierella, Mucor, Myrothecium, Penicillium, Phialophora, Xylaria, decomposition, dominance, enzyme activity, fungus, human activity, microbial community, mineralization, morphology, soil ecosystem, soil microorganism, species diversity, species richness, taxonomy, temperature tolerance, tundra},
