  keywords={Cellulose, Ectomycorrhizal fungi, Nothofagus, pH, Phosphatase, Temperature, Cells, Cellulose, Fungi, Ph, Pyrometry, Descolea antarctica, Fungi, Nothofagus, Nothofagus obliqua, Cell culture, Cellulose, pH effects, Temperature measurement, amylase, cellulase, phosphatase, article, beech, controlled study, Descolea antarctica, enzyme activity, fungal strain, greenhouse, inoculation, mycelium, nonhuman, Nothofagus obliqua, plant growth, reforestation, seedling, Ectomycorrhizal strains, Mycelial strains, Phosphatases, Fungi},
